title: Who Will Make the Leap In 2022?
description:
Kevin, Nora, Steven, and Ben go down their list of people and teams that will make a leap for the upcoming season.

Host: Kevin Clark, Nora Princiotti, Steven Ruiz, and Ben Solak
Associate Producer: Stefan Anderson
Additional Production Supervision: Arjuna Ramgopal
